## ğŸ“Œ Exit Status Codes (Important in scripting)

* `0` â†’ Success
* `1` â†’ General error
* `2` â†’ Misuse of shell command
* `126` â†’ Command not executable
* `127` â†’ Command not found
* `130` â†’ Script terminated with Ctrl+C

Check exit status of the last command with:

```bash
